Name: Total time between Manuscript Export Succeeded and Awaiting Assignment to Batch in cases where SW-Reviewer Agreed occurred

Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Elapsed time between SW-Reviewer Agreed and Awaiting Assignment to Batch across all process variants

Name: Average waiting time to the Awaiting Assignment to Batch following Manuscript Export Succeeded
